Cons I can think of-

 - Cannot serialize the state as JSON (easily fixed with a Todo.toJSON() method).
 - Doesn&#39;t follow normal pattern where setState operates on a key/value pair.
 - Calling todo.setText() might be confusing since it doesn&#39;t update state.

