Thanks to very patient help and guidance from Brian Malehorn, I have a functioning solution.

Install the [macros extension](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=geddski.macros).

Add to user settings:

```json
    &quot;macros&quot;: {
        &quot;findNextAndFocusText&quot;: [
            &quot;editor.action.nextMatchFindAction&quot;,
            &quot;closeFindWidget&quot;
        ]
    }
```

Add to keybindings:

```json
    {
        &quot;key&quot;: &quot;cmd+g&quot;,
        &quot;command&quot;: &quot;macros.findNextAndFocusText&quot;,
        &quot;when&quot;: &quot;editorFocus&quot;
    }
```

